{"tid":542601,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[An]各巴絲打、我整隻GAME終於出得啦!!!","createTime":"2018-01-27T15:48:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T16:05:52.000Z","uid":37698,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1dddd5ad98a9270afa14e6802536aa3830405410","tid":542601,"uid":37698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:48:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/C10rVm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FC10rVm.png&h=fc9ef199&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n早出既唔刪檔封測，雖然好多人未玩先屌，但亦有好多巴絲打俾左好多寶貴既意見我！<br />\n最初其實我自己都無咩信心，但後來越改越加多野，我越來越有信心，亦收到唔少玩家既好評！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n隻game叫「魔幻三國」，會係<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">1月29日下晝2點正式開服!!!</span></strong><br />\n宜家搞緊「事前登錄」活動，依2日註冊acc，就<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">送500寶石+祕卡黃月英！</span></strong><br />\n希望大家可以來玩下，然後俾更多意見我去改進，我一定會做到最好！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>▲遊戲特色</strong></span><br />\n－大家熟識既三國題材，玩法簡單易上手，希望做到親民、休閒<br />\n－5vs5對戰，可以指定唔同人、或者同朋友對戰<br />\n－策略類遊戲，重視陣形、企位、技能、武將更種配搭<br />\n－畫師手繪既日系魔幻畫風，希望歷史題材都可以吸引更多女玩家<br />\n－初版收錄超過100多個武將，可以滿足鍾意收集三國武將既你<br />\n－有組隊cost限制，絕對公平既遊戲，唔係課金向既game<br />\n－可以課金(唯一收入)，但絕對唔會課金先勁，唔會影響遊戲公平性<br />\n－每個星期都會有全server玩家大混戰既活動，送大量寶石<br />\n－每個月必定至少出一次大更新，出8個新武將，將來仲會有新系統<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">▲利申</span></strong><br />\n因為係3個人既獨立製作，無錢宣傳，所以唯有係Facebook同論壇宣傳<br />\n論壇用既係Discuz模版、網址係阿里雲申請的<br />\n暫時只有Android版，將來會再出ios版(可以暫時用模擬器玩，官網有)<br />\n<br />\n遊戲官網　<a href=\"http://1m3k.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F1m3k.com%2F&d=TCECO9EFxHjleQyVYmg%2BMQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=b571b984\" target=\"_blank\">http://1m3k.com/</a><br />\nFacebook　<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1m3kd/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1m3kd%2F&d=TCECO9EFxHjleQyVYmg%2BMQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=9cc566cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1m3kd/</a>"},{"pid":"72704b0cb21e3aeca97e5bf49841c73131cd04fe","tid":542601,"uid":37698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:49:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>《入門攻略》</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/J4YIxV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FJ4YIxV.jpg&h=b72b4317&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">▲開始篇</span></strong><br />\n「新手教學」3選1的初始武將可以隨便選、因為3個都差不多，新手期間過渡用。<br />\n蔡文姬技能是群體治療，新手恩物。<br />\n關平強化攻和防，不錯的傷害輸出。<br />\n黃蓋強化防和策，做主將非常耐打。<br />\n<br />\n完成「新手教學」後，建議先升級建築，首選「國庫」，先提高米糧上限。<br />\n小提示：建築每次升級都會將米糧回滿，所以升級前記得把米糧先用完！<br />\n&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;建築系統&amp;lt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;<br />\n<a href=\"http://1m3k.com/bbs/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F1m3k.com%2Fbbs%2Fforum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D3&d=TCECO9EFxHjleQyVYmg%2BMQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=87f1d96f\" target=\"_blank\">http://1m3k.com/bbs/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=3</a><br />\n<br />\n有多餘的金幣，當然是用來「轉蛋」，提升自己的隊伍。<br />\n小提示：新得到的武將，會先存放在「保管武將」欄，移到「備戰武將」欄才能使用。<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/htn8M0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2Fhtn8M0.jpg&h=3e9296c1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">▲出陣篇</span></strong><br />\n1.主線關卡<br />\n必打！最優先打！<br />\n每個關卡的第4關和第8關都會送一張卡(有金卡和銀卡)，快速變強的捷徑！<br />\n&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;主線關卡&amp;lt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;<br />\n<a href=\"http://1m3k.com/bbs/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=28\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F1m3k.com%2Fbbs%2Fforum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D28&d=TCECO9EFxHjleQyVYmg%2BMQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=ffe0c36e\" target=\"_blank\">http://1m3k.com/bbs/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=28</a><br />\n<br />\n2.排名對戰<br />\n每日打打寶石！每日首勝有30寶石送！排名前100也有寶石獎勵！<br />\n想和朋友或其他玩家對戰，可以用「指名對戰」(不消耗米糧)。<br />\n<br />\n3.探險和討賊<br />\n快速消耗米糧的方法，沒空時、或者米糧用不完時就探險吧！遇到女賊能獲得寶石獎勵!!<br />\n<br />\n4.銅雀台<br />\n打材料專用，只在指定時間出現，每次出現半小時，每日首勝送3個龍玉<br />\n9、13、17、21點打裝備，11、15、19、23點打武將<br />\n<br />\n5.主題競技場<br />\n一星期一次的大型活動，星期二至四報名，星期五到日舉行，可以獲得大量寶石和限定祕卡!!!<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/FxLq4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FFxLq4e.jpg&h=8f990e55&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>▲變強篇</strong></span><br />\n1.武將選擇<br />\n帶強力攻擊技的武將打npc很實用，例如關卡1.8送的張梁、3.8送的華雄<br />\n治療有一個就夠，例如初始送的蔡琰、糜夫人都很好用<br />\n如果主將有&amp;lt;主將技&amp;gt;威力會更強，例如關卡7.8送的公孫瓚<br />\n&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;武將庫&amp;lt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;(按武將名可以查看詳情)<br />\n<a href=\"http://1m3k.com:8080//optimist/o-s/cardSearch.action\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F1m3k.com%3A8080%2F%2Foptimist%2Fo-s%2FcardSearch.action&d=TCECO9EFxHjleQyVYmg%2BMQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=f77f829b\" target=\"_blank\">http://1m3k.com:8080//optimist/o-s/cardSearch.action</a><br />\n&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;戰鬥知識&amp;lt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;<br />\n<a href=\"http://1m3k.com/bbs/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F1m3k.com%2Fbbs%2Fforum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D7&d=TCECO9EFxHjleQyVYmg%2BMQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=d7026fe0\" target=\"_blank\">http://1m3k.com/bbs/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=7</a><br />\n<br />\n2.強化武將<br />\n核心武將建議先升到Lv.10（經驗值最少、效益最大）<br />\n攻：普攻傷害、物理技能傷害<br />\n防：減傷、行動優先次序<br />\n策：策攻技能傷害、恢復量、技能成功率、技能集氣速度<br />\n<br />\n3.裝備製作<br />\n將多餘的裝備合成上去<br />\n<br />\n4.拜訪好友<br />\n每日互相拜訪可以獲得米糧和大量獎勵<br />\n<br />\n5.做成就<br />\n可以獲得大量獎勵，尤其寶石"},{"pid":"dee57fd467781ebfb12a4d67844e623b2aa58cdd","tid":542601,"uid":9125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:50:10.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cda9ed1cf58b5908de727fd522b4487ca155a6d","tid":542601,"uid":23107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:51:18.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7d1e7beaf8ebba745aeb58470ff21c1491d4329","tid":542601,"uid":37698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:52:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/gmKy1n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FgmKy1n.jpg&h=58db0aa7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"80366a1789a42ef2133acd7c61bf2a96a125ace4","tid":542601,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7d1e7beaf8ebba745aeb58470ff21c1491d4329","tid":542601,"uid":37698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:52:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/gmKy1n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FgmKy1n.jpg&h=58db0aa7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T16:16:58.000Z","msg":"塊面好包啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef8f76fe1050693d1b1f2aebfec06d3d2771ae11","tid":542601,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T16:22:03.000Z","msg":"三國 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2696e51f5ee519ae989664e7b419b151c7d3ce6","tid":542601,"uid":149018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T18:32:32.000Z","msg":"Ios呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw幾有興趣<br />\n同埋隻game想搵幫手比意見or gm可以搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96115ad00a707895d23b167a0e9d1f1a5706bf17","tid":542601,"uid":37698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T16:05:22.000Z","msg":"新的技能特效 更華麗更霸氣!!!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/0PHgtV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F0PHgtV.gif&h=adde54f6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/MT0ia8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FMT0ia8.gif&h=2a1e45c1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/G78pPl.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FG78pPl.gif&h=c6d3ffd5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/F7CPQD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FF7CPQD.gif&h=b4f39d97&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/kpe0LA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2Fkpe0LA.gif&h=aefb02c5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/Ikihb2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FIkihb2.gif&h=c8662eb0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c3061aa78bfbf08ecfac43555cdb1af2a877806","tid":542601,"uid":37698,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T16:05:52.000Z","msg":"開服7大活動送大禮!!!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>1.註冊遊戲送50寶石!!</strong></span><br />\n　前3000名註冊的玩家即送50寶石(發送到遊戲禮箱)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2.充值加送50%寶石!!</strong></span><br />\n　前300名在商城充值任何金額、會額外再送50%寶石，充值越多送越多。<br />\n　位置：遊戲內「商城」充值<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>3.特別「開服轉蛋」登場</strong></span><br />\n　500寶石一次連抽5張卡，保證至少有1張品質是銀或金!!<br />\n　位置：遊戲內「轉蛋」開服轉蛋<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>4.建築Lv.5獎勵</strong></span><br />\n　2月28日前只要以下建築達到Lv.5就能獲得相應獎勵。<br />\n　學府Lv.5：10張「獎券轉蛋」券<br />\n　巿集Lv.5：200寶石<br />\n　工房Lv.5：20個裝備盒<br />\n　城門Lv.5：6000金幣<br />\n　＃獎勵會郵寄到玩家「禮箱」。<br />\n　＃由於是公測活動的延續，公測帳號不會重複獲得獎勵<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>5.成就「初心者」</strong></span><br />\n　2月28日前主城等級達到Lv.10，就能獲得成就「初心者」。<br />\n　建築等級每升1級，主城等級就會加1。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>6.Facebook分享送10個裝備盒!!</strong></span><br />\n　將於1月29日公布，詳情請留意《魔幻三國》Facebook專頁。<br />\n　<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1m3kd/]https://www.facebook.com/1m3kd/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1m3kd%2F%5Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1m3kd%2F&d=TCECO9EFxHjleQyVYmg%2BMQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=5b345cb1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1m3kd/]https://www.facebook.com/1m3kd/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>7.撰寫攻略文活動</strong></span><br />\n　在官網論壇撰寫本遊戲的攻略。<br />\n　只要獲得優秀賞，就能獲得寶石獎勵!!<br />\n　活動詳情會於2月1日在論壇公布，請留意論壇。<br />\n　<a href=\"http://1m3k.com/bbs/forum.php]http://1m3k.com/bbs/forum.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F1m3k.com%2Fbbs%2Fforum.php%5Dhttp%3A%2F%2F1m3k.com%2Fbbs%2Fforum.php&d=TCECO9EFxHjleQyVYmg%2BMQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=d7e2f73e\" target=\"_blank\">http://1m3k.com/bbs/forum.php]http://1m3k.com/bbs/forum.php</a>"}]}